Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.42,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}進め　弾け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.71,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どのみち混むでしょ
