Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:47.09,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}rockを奏でろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.65,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}遠くを見据えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.68,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}息継ぎさえできない街の中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.60,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}星空が最高の舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:07.39,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}カラスたちカーカーと鳴くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.01,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつも思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.93,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつ寝てるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:20.23,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　あたしも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.82,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}song for　歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:31.30,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}rockを響かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:36.90,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}crowを歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.53,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでこんなところに居る？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.22,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そう言う奴もいた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.99,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}うるさいことだけ言うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:57.61,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}漆黒の羽にさらわれて消えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.45,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}全力でもう倒れそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.41,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}指もすり切れて痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.03,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}でもね　演るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.04,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}今夜もビッグなストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:43.71,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　ここから
