Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:47.09,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}rock 演奏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.65,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}紧盯着远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.68,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在这片刻喘息也没有的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.60,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}星空是最棒的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:07.39,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}乌鸦们也哇哇叫个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.01,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我总是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.93,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}难道它们不用睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:20.23,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　我也如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.82,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}song for　开始歌唱
